author: Mitch Stephens
title: De La Salle routs Long Beach Poly 52-6
text:
Photo: Michael Macor, The Chronicle Spartans' Isaiah Randle, 34 goes in for a second quarter touchdown with Jackrabbits' De' Andre Pierce, 4 covering as De La Salle High School takes on Polytechnic High School in Concord, Calif., on Fri. October 16, 2015. Spartans' Isaiah Randle, 34 goes in for a second quarter touchdown...
For fans, photographers and videographers alike, De La Salle’s 18-play, 71-yard touchdown drive to start the third quarter was anything but pretty.
